  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}I'm really sorry...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}{f 5 13 18 15 1}I just feel bad since I'm the one who wanted to hang out...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}But actually... my mom fainted.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}I'm at the hospital right now.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}They said it's exhaustion... since she works from morning till night.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}Dammit! It's all my fault![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_018_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}And my mom—she's trying to leave! She says we can't afford the medical bills.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}Goddammit! Why can't I do anything!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}I'm useless! I'm just another one of her problems.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}...I'm sorry about all that. I... I don't wanna be a problem for you, too.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}But I'm glad you were the one to hear me out.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 115 90 -1 68 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Talking about this kinda helped.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="MND_020_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Hayase is going through some awful times.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}He opened up to me about it,[n]and I feel like we're closer now.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
